Russian TV Ads May Cost 20% More Next Year, Kommersant Says

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-12T05:02:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-12/russian-tv-ads-may-cost-20-more-next-year-kommersant-says.html
Advertisements on Russian
television may cost 20 percent more on average next year,
Kommersant reported, citing Sergei Vasilyev, the general
director of Video International.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow 
 sbierman1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
